      "text": "to describe the concept of marriage, not"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 306920.0,
      "text": "your fashion sense. Concept is another"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 306920.0,
      "end_time": 308280.0,
      "text": "word for an idea or belief."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 308280.0,
      "end_time": 311219.0,
      "text": "So an archaic concept is an old-fashioned"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 311220.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 313440.0,
      "text": "Neil: Our next expression was"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 313440.0,
      "end_time": 315150.0,
      "text": "commitment phobe."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 315150.0,
      "end_time": 317000.0,
      "text": "We use this phrase to talk about someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 317000.0,
      "end_time": 319600.0,
      "text": "who is scared of the idea of a long-term"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 319620.0,
      "end_time": 321880.0,
      "text": "relationship because they see it as giving"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 321880.0,
      "end_time": 322838.0,
      "text": "up some freedoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 322838.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "You're obviously a compliment phobe!"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327256.0,
      "text": "You're afraid of saying nice things about"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 327256.0,
      "end_time": 328994.0,
      "text": "someone so you always say something"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 328995.0,
      "end_time": 329690.0,
      "text": "nasty as well!"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 329690.0,
      "end_time": 331450.0,
      "text": "Rob: I said I was sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 331450.0,
      "end_time": 334527.0,
      "text": "Neil: And finally we had the adjective"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 334528.0,
      "end_time": 335500.0,
      "text": "stabilising."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 335500.0,
      "end_time": 337780.0,
      "text": "Something that is stable is strong and"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 337780.0,
      "end_time": 339580.0,
      "text": "something that makes something strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 339581.0,
      "end_time": 341340.0,
      "text": "can be described as stabilising."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 341340.0,
      "end_time": 343340.0,
      "text": "Dan expressed his belief that"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 343340.0,
      "end_time": 345460.0,
      "text": "marriage had a stabilising effect on"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 345460.0,
      "end_time": 346280.0,
      "text": "society."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 346280.0,
      "end_time": 348619.0,
      "text": "Well, that's it for this programme. For"
